\c 35
\s Mufaro uchava paZiyoni
\p
\v 1 Renje nenyika yakaoma zvichafara; sango richafara kwazvo, richatumbuka seruva.
\v 2 Richatumbuka zvizhinji, nokufara kwazvo nomufaro nokuimba; richapiwa kunaka kukuru kweRebhanoni, noukomba bweKarimeri neSharoni; vachaona kunaka kukuru kwaJehovha, ihwo ukomba hwaMwari wedu.
\p
\v 3 Simbisai maoko asine simba, mutsigire mabvi anodedera.
\v 4 Iti kuna vane moyo inotya, "Simbai, musatya! Tarirai, Mwari wenyu achauya nokutsiva, nokuripira kwaMwari; achauya achikuponesai."
\v 5 Ipapo meso amapofu achasvinudzwa, nenzeve dzematsi dzichadziurwa.
\v 6 Ipapo anokamhina achakwakuka senondo, rurimi rwembeveve rwuchaimba nokuti mvura zhinji ichadzutuka murenje, nehova dzemvura mugwenga.
\v 7 Jecha, rinopisa, richashanduka dziva, nevhu, rine nyota, zvitubu zvemvura; paugaro hwamakava, paaivata, pachava nouswa, netsanga nenhokwe.
\v 8 Ipapo pachava nomugwagwa, nenzira, ichanzi, "Nzira youtsvene;" ane tsvina haangafambi nayo, asi ichava yavo; vanofamba nayo, kunyange ari mapenzi, havangarashiki.
\p
\v 9 Hapangavi neshumba, kunyange nechikara hachingafambipo; hazvingawanikwipo, asi vakadzikunurwa ndivo vachafambapo;
\v 10 vakasunungurwa vaJehovha vachadzoka, vachasvika Ziyoni vachiimba, mufaro usingaperi uchava pamisoro yavo; vachawana mufaro nomoyo muchena, kuchema nokusuwa kuchatiza.
